,"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"……嗯。完全可以啊！\n从那天以后，我比以前更加喜欢做饭了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"memorial176-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"果然人们吃的津津有味的样子\n很能让人拿出干劲对吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"memorial176-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"而且，那都是和我们素未谋面的人们，\n就更让人高兴了☆　因为，对饭菜的\n称赞中没有客套的成分，不是吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"memorial176-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"……嗯！\n一句话来说的话，就是特别开心","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"memorial176-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"帮完忙之后，\n和绯玛丽聊了聊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"mo